api_list.name: /extract
api_list.description: This endpoint seamlessly processes incoming text alongside an array of specified entities, extracting their data, and efficiently returns the results in JSON format for seamless integration into your applications. Checkout API Docs 👇
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://jsonextract-pro.p.rapidapi.com/api/v1/extract"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "jsonextract-pro.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
